    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3 in concours condition. This example features the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering power through six individual throttle bodies and a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. Mechanically flawless, the dual-VANOS system has been meticulously serviced, and the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced. The chassis retains its factory rigidity with zero suspension bushing deflection. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, the paint depth is consistent across all panels with no oxidation. A true driver\u2019s specimen with a documented service history and a limited-slip differential that remains tight and responsive.",
